<subSubSection id="C34F8499FFA0936BFF25F995FDF4F8A1" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BEAD712FFA0936BFF25F995FDF4F8A1" blockId="8.[151,1437,289,1900]" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFF25F995FEF8F9E5" bold="true" box="[199,315,1550,1576]" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFEA1F995FCB7F9E5" authority="Grouvelle, 1903" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1903" box="[323,884,1550,1576]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrocastanea" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFEA1F995FD77F9E5" box="[323,692,1550,1576]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">Aethina (Aethina) nigrocastanea</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4AAE3FFA0936BFD5EF995FCB7F9E5" author="Grouvelle, A." box="[700,884,1550,1576]" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" pagination="108 - 124" refId="ref10668" refString="Grouvelle, A. (1903) Clavicornes de l'Inde septentrionale recoltes par M. Harmand. Nitidulidae. - Colydiidae. - Cucujidae. - Monotomidae. - Dryopidae. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, 72, 108 - 124." type="journal article" year="1903">Grouvelle, 1903</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was synonymised with 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFB64F995FE8DF981" authority="Grouvelle, 1894" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1894" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicina" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFB64F995FA5FF9E5" box="[1158,1436,1550,1576]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">Aethina (Aethina) vicina</emphasis>
Grouvelle, 1894
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4AAE3FFA0936BFE98F9A9FD86F980" author="Kirejtshuk, A. G." box="[378,581,1586,1613]" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" pagination="44 - 82" refId="ref10996" refString="Kirejtshuk, A. G. (1986) Revision of the genus Aethina Er. (Coleoptera, Nitidulidae) of the fauna of the Oriental and Palaearctic regions. Trudy Zoologischeskogo Instituta AN SSSR, 140, 44 - 82. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1986">Kirejtshuk (1986)</bibRefCitation>
. Both the species are available in the reference collection of ZSI (identified by Grouvelle). We dissected out the male genitalia of the former species and compared it with the line diagram of the male genitalia of 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFE6AF9E1FD1DF959" authority="Grouvelle, 1894" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1894" box="[392,734,1658,1684]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicina" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFE6AF9E1FDDCF959" box="[392,543,1658,1684]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">A. (A.) vicina</emphasis>
Grouvelle, 1894
</taxonomicName>
as given by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4AAE3FFA0936BFC92F9E1FBF3F959" author="Kirejtshuk, A. G." box="[880,1072,1658,1684]" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" pagination="44 - 82" refId="ref10996" refString="Kirejtshuk, A. G. (1986) Revision of the genus Aethina Er. (Coleoptera, Nitidulidae) of the fauna of the Oriental and Palaearctic regions. Trudy Zoologischeskogo Instituta AN SSSR, 140, 44 - 82. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1986">Kirejtshuk, 1986</bibRefCitation>
. We arrived at a conclusion that although morphologically very similar, 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFDB6F905FD2AF975" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1894" box="[596,745,1694,1720]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicina" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFDB6F905FD2AF975" box="[596,745,1694,1720]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">A. (A.) vicina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFC9FF905FBAEF975" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1903" box="[893,1133,1694,1720]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrocastanea" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFC9FF905FBAEF975" box="[893,1133,1694,1720]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">A. (A.) nigrocastanea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the body being blackish [vs. body chocolate-brown in 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFE10F959FD2BF911" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1903" box="[498,744,1730,1756]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrocastanea" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFE10F959FD2BF911" box="[498,744,1730,1756]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">A. (A.) nigrocastanea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
], shape of tegmen of male genitalia with truncate apex [
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFA9CF958FA5FF911" box="[1406,1436,1731,1756]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">vs.</emphasis>
tegmen of male genitalia with rounded apex in 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFD4BF97DFC5AF8CD" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1903" box="[681,921,1766,1792]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrocastanea" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFD4BF97DFC5AF8CD" box="[681,921,1766,1792]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">A. (A.) nigrocastanea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
], shape of median lobe of male genitalia with pointed apex and bifid flap situated rather far from the apex [
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFCACF890FCAFF8E9" box="[846,876,1803,1828]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">vs.</emphasis>
median lobe of male genitalia with truncate apex and bifid flap extending beyond the apex in 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFD7BF8B5FC4DF885" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1903" box="[665,910,1838,1864]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrocastanea" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFD7BF8B5FC4DF885" box="[665,910,1838,1864]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">A. (A.) nigrocastanea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
]. The specific status of 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFA0936BFB45F8B5FEC4F8A1" authority="Grouvelle" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1903" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrocastanea" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFA0936BFB45F8B5FA5FF885" box="[1191,1436,1838,1864]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="541">A. (A.) nigrocastanea</emphasis>
Grouvelle
</taxonomicName>
is therefore re-established.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
